      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;According to the Magical Law of Constants, attempting to make a spell permanent is impossible, as the spell will rapidly drain like water through a sieve. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige does not believe this to be true. She has been pursuing spell permanence for her entire magical career, seeking to give herself an ideal body that brings her comfort. Along with her close friend Raina, she has come to the City State of Steadfast, only seeking to stay the night. A late night breakthrough will turn not only their lives, but the entire world on its head.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;div class="chapter-title"&gt;Chapter 1 &amp;#8211; Magical Law&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="chp_raw" id="chp_raw"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Magical Law of Constants&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“It is well known among scholars of the magical arts, that magic is a volatile and unruly energy, which can only be controlled for short periods of time. Magic can be shaped into a form that we desire in the form of a spell, but the spell cannot be held for lengthy periods, without causing a great deal of harm to the caster in question.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In a similar manner, magic cannot be used to fundamentally change an object. A diver can give themselves gills to breathe underwater, a fighter can grow their muscles, and one can change iron to gold. Invariably, the magic will leave the affected object, and the changes will fade. Despite our best efforts, magic refuses to be contained.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Alchemy, being a physical art, can change the nature of an object. Due to the exorbitant costs associated with acquiring the reagents required for the art, it is limited to only the very wealthy.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;Raina’s green eyes glazed over, the kitsune’s tail idly waving behind herself, indicating just how much (or how little) she was paying attention to Paige’s lecture. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“So what is that all supposed to mean then?” She asked in a bored tone.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige’s cheeks puffed out adorably, and she tossed the book towards her lover, who deftly caught it with her tail. The mage crossed her arms and continued pouting, which only brought a devious grin to Raina’s face.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Y-You were asking me why I use alchemy tablets to change my appearance, instead of my magic. Well that’s why!”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Leaning upside down on the couch, Raina idly read through the passage that Paige had just read. The mage began to gently comb her hair, untangling weeks old knots, allowing it to spread out and floof up properly. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“&lt;em&gt;An enduring mystery among scholars is why alchemical components retain their magical properties over long periods of time.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;Paige peaked her head out from the bathroom, to see Raina reading from a passage much later in the book. The mage humphed, and Raina smirked again before continuing.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“&lt;em&gt;Magic absorbed within many natural components can be distilled and used in alchemic practices to create many advanced technological wonders that we enjoy, such as airships, trains and other advanced machinery. There are many theories as to how this process works, but no consensus has been reached. Many faiths across the realms believe it to be the work of their God, who deemed that magic is a divine power, unable to be used by mortals except for very brief periods. Entities that are already magical in nature, such as Fae, Devils and Kitsune can change their shape at will as magic is a part of their nature.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;The mage stared dubiously at Raina, who shimmered, then shifted into her human form of a sultry redhead, with a devious smirk. “Seems a tad unfair, doesn’t it?”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige’s shoulders slumped and she held down her comb, before nodding and letting out a sigh. “That’s the exact objective of my research, Raina. I want to uncover the reasons behind this phenomenon, and perhaps find a way to break it.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Raina glanced Paige up and down, then nodded her head. “I remember, it’s just… not something I’ve thought of very much. Changing myself is just as natural for me, as breathing is for you. And you know…” She smirked deviously, before shifting back to her natural form. “It’s not unheard of for humans to shed their mortality, and become magical entities themselves. I could… Help you with that.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A shiver ran up Paige’s spine at the suggestion, and not for the first time, she considered the offer. In the end, as always, she shook her head.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“I’m sorry, but I don’t think that would be the right path for me. I want… I want to uncover this mystery. Both for myself, and for other people in the world who might feel the same way I do.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Raina sighed, and sat back up on the couch properly, her tail swishing behind her. “I did always love that stubbornness, just make sure that you do not break yourself before you find the answer.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The mage sighed as she slipped off the towel from her bath, leaving her standing naked in front of the inn’s mirror. Reaching into her leather knapsack, she retrieved a carefully cloth wrapped package that she unfurled with gentle reverence. Inside were fifteen tablets, crafted by the town’s alchemist, Hazel, who kindly made them affordable to her merchant family.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Gingerly holding one of the brown tablets, she looked in the mirror and winced. Rationing the tablets was not the best choice, but it was the best course of action to take until they could find a new supplier. Besides, it wasn’t as if anyone besides Raina would see her out on the road, and Raina…&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Raina… do you think I’m… pretty?”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The fox girl flicked her ears and looked up from the book, seeing Paige bare, holding a tablet and with wet tears in her eyes. She set the tome aside and smiled, gently approaching her beloved, and pulling her into a fluffy hug. Paige leaned into the hug, sighing as a burden she’d been holding inside of her dissipated.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“I’ll give you an honest answer Paige. You are the most beautiful girl I’ve met on my travels, both internally and externally. I love everything about you, from your fluffy hair, to your flawless skin…” She gently ran a hand over Paige’s umber colored skin, who let out a little squeak in response to the stimulation.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“I don’t love your facial hairs, or your body hairs, because they cause you a lot of distress. But it doesn’t make me love &lt;em&gt;you&lt;/em&gt; any less my dear.” Raina sealed her statements with a gentle kiss on Paige’s lips, and the mage swooned in her lover’s embrace.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“O-Okay… thank you.” She managed to squeak out.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Raina tenderly patted Paige’s cheek, and her hand idly wandered down below between Paige’s legs, not seeking to stimulate but to emphasize. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Have you decided whether you want to keep this or not yet?”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige hesitated as Raina gently held her little cocklet, and shrugged. “I-I’m not sure… I used to think I wanted a vagina more than anything, but ever since I met you, I’ve come to love it more.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The kitsune grinned, and gave a very light stroke. “You love what I can do to it, you mean?”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The little mageling sucked in a breath at the light, yet stimulating touch and then let out a giggle. “That too. But I more meant that we’ve been enjoying our time together with it, and it’d be a shame to lose it, you know?”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The foxgirl nodded, and lowered her hand, to which Paige seemed to let out a disappointed whine in response, which brought another toothy smirk to Raina’s face.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Well don’t forget that it’s about &lt;em&gt;your &lt;/em&gt;comfort, love. Whatever you decide on, I’ll be fine with it. Besides… I’m sure I can think of a few ways to play with you if you get a vagina~” She finished her sentence with a wink.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Between the smirks, the winks and the gentle touches, Paige was feeling stimulated and loved. It made her knees wobbly and her skin break out in goosebumps. Raina smirked again and gently kissed Paige on the forehead.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Go take your medicine dear, and then come meet me on the bed. That’s…” She leaned in closer, until she was looming over Paige. “An order.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The mage shuddered at the command, and resolutely nodded her head in response. “Y-Yes, right away!”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As she turned to return to the bathroom, the foxgirl playfully cupped her pert rear, which caused Paige to moan loudly.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Good girl~”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige hurried into the bathroom, and shut the door behind her, though it did little to stifle the giggles coming from the other side. Huffing her cheeks again, she returned to the mirror, and put the chewable tablet in her mouth. The sweet taste of cocoa powder, cinnamon and sugar flooded her mouth, Hazel always had a penchant for making medicine go down easier with sugar.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige enjoyed watching the changes happen to her body, and the long pause since the last dosage was sure to make this change even more intense and enjoyable. She still remembered the first time she’d taken the tablets as one of the best moments of her life. Memories mingled with the present as she remembered, and witnessed her nearly flat chest begin to grow. Burgeoning soft flesh filled out behind her erect nipples, quickly growing in size. More hot tears began to form in her vision as she watched them grow, she’d missed them so much.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Elsewhere in her body, subtler changes began to take shape, and formed her into the reflection that made her feel so euphoric. All the hair below her eyebrows began to fall away, forming a dark layer on the floor. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I’ll have to sweep that up later.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;It could wait though, because one of her favorite parts was coming up. The redistribution of fat was something that many people would register, but not fully recognize until you pointed it out to them. She loved how when she took the tablets, her hips flared out, her bottom became even perkier, and her waist pinched in more ever so slightly. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;While her facial features did not change as drastically, the fat redistribution made her face round out a little bit from the sharp angles that defined her born features. She hated it so much that when they traveled she would always be wearing a face scarf to cover up the stubble and her features.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Sighing in sweet relief, the heat began to fade as her body settled into its new appearance, much closer to what she envisioned for herself. As always, she reached up to gently touch the mirror and admire the changes. Hazel really was an amazing apothecary, and Paige hoped she had made it out of their hometown safely. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;She wasn’t entirely sure how the pills worked, but she could not doubt their efficacy, nor the positive effects it had on her overall state of being. It was like a great weight had been lifted off her chest, in part because of the new weights they now carried. Her entire body felt lighter, and easier to inhabit. More hot tears streamed down her face as she continued to stare at her own reflection, truly seeing who she was for the first time in weeks.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Exiting the bathroom, she stood in front of her kitsune lover, and struck a pose. The kitsune gave a bright smile, and rose from the couch, letting herself wrap up her lovely mageling in a tight hug. Paige swooned as Raina held her tenderly, and one of her soft fuzzy hands gently pet Paige’s newly softened cheek.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“You are always beautiful to me, but you shine the brightest after your treatment.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige blushed at the sincerity of the compliment, and tried to look down, but Raina tilted her chin back up and ever so slightly shook her head.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Don’t hide that pretty face of yours, love. I want to admire it for as long as I can.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The mage’s face grew so hot that her ears began to burn a bright pink. Mirthful giggles escaped from the sly kitsune, as a hand wandered down, and cupped Paige’s pert bottom, and squeezed. Just as the mage let out a moan, Raina’s mouth was lightly nipping on her ear, eliciting a desperate moan.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“I know just what you need after you have your medicine. Oh, don’t make that desperate expression, I wouldn’t be so cruel as to leave you hanging.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige squealed as Raina hooked her arms under Paige, and lifted her up. She gently tossed her onto the bed, and the mage let out another embarrassed squeal. With a confident smirk, the Kitsune crawled across the bed, to loom over her embarrassed lover.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Now then… what shall I do with you?”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Paige shivered, knowing that whatever Raina decided to do, she would love every second of it.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
